''' While designing a system it is always a good practice to think in terms of Top-Bottom '''

1. Will try to visualize the GUI of the system, it will give us sense of what all features the system will have.
2. Once we have some picture in our mind, how our system will look like for user, will get idea of what all classes
   and APIs server app will need to have in order to full fill GUI request needs.
3. Giving a thought of data-bases will also help to understand how class will interact with DB and what kind of data
   each table will have

